  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and garlic; sauté until translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add carrots and potatoes, cooking for 5 minutes while stirring.",
    "Stir in tomato paste, thyme, salt, and pepper; cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add seitan and vegetable broth, bring to a gentle boil.",
    "Add bay leaf, reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer 20 minutes until vegetables are tender.",
    "Remove the bay leaf and stir in peas; simmer 5 more minutes.",
    "In a small saucepan, whisk together sumac, maple syrup, soy sauce, lemon juice, and a splash of water; heat until thickened, about 3–4 minutes.",
    "Pour the glaze into the stew and stir to coat; simmer 2 minutes.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped parsley.",
